## ✅ Cleanup Results

- **`job/data-sync-job`** → `NotFound` ✅
- **`pod/data-sync-job-pod`** → removed ✅
- **`data-sync-storage` (PVC)** → still `Bound` ✅ (untouched)
- **`db-credentials` (Secret)** → still present ✅ (untouched)
- **`data-sync-job-v2-active`** → still running ✅ (untouched)

Deletion used `--cascade=none` (default), so shared resources were never at risk. The disk pressure on `worker-node-03` should begin to resolve as the stuck pod is gone.
